      Handles DELETE requests to the "/scenarios/{title}/step/{stepLevel}" endpoint and deletes a step from the scenario with the given title.

      Handles GET requests to the "/scenario/renameactor/{oldactor}/{newactor}" endpoint and renames the given actor in the scenario provided in the request body.
      Scenario GetDownloadScenarioController.getScenario​(String title)
      Handles GET requests to the "/scenario/{title}" endpoint and returns the scenario with the given title from the storage.
      Scenario GetScenarioLevelCutController.getScenarioLevelCut​(String title, Integer maxLevel)
      Handles GET requests to the "/scenarios/{title}/levelcut/{maxLevel}" endpoint and returns a truncated version of the scenario with the given title for a stored Scenario.
